  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your connection to the skies above is so strong that your feet barely touch the ground. At 1st level, you no longer leave tracks.</p>\n<p>At 5th level, you can hover up to 6 inches above the ground or even above liquid surfaces, as if levitating.</p>\n<p>At 10th level, you gain the ability to fly, as per the spell, for a number of minutes per day equal to your oracle level. This duration does not need to be consecutive, but it must be spent in 1-minute increments.</p>"
